# API & Data Fetching
- Validate all incoming request bodies with Zod before processing
- Return consistent JSON shapes: `{ data, error, status }`
- Use Server Actions for form mutations — not client-side fetch calls
- Use TanStack Query for client-side data fetching and caching
- Never expose sensitive env vars to the client (prefix with NEXT_PUBLIC_ only intentionally)
- Rate-limit all public API routes
- Always handle and log errors — never swallow them silently